public class NexmlViewer
extends mesquite.lib.duties.DataWindowAssistantI

The main class for MesquiteNexmlViewer, where NeXML annotations are generated by pulling data from the hashmaps in URIMap. Also automatically generates Graphviz dot graphs based on the NeXML annotations.

Version:
2009-08-15
Author:
